# Allowlist build context (build from repo root): ONLY what games2/Dockerfile
# COPYs. New top-level domains stay out of the context (and off the deploy
# critical path) until the Dockerfile actually bakes them in.
*
!games2
games2/node_modules
games2/client/dist
games2/**/*.tsbuildinfo
games2/.data
!objects
!characters2
!tiles2
!maps2
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
*.log
